<i>(Filtered to help with inaccuracies with low numbers).</i><br>
<b>Formatting</b>:<br>
stddev &gt;2: <i>controversial (italic)</i>.<br>
&lt;10 ratings: small.<br>
Wettbewerb: <b>bold</b><br>
</small><p>

EOF
